                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2358Sirach">ሲራክ፡ ወልደ፡ ዓልዓዛር</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ትምህርተ፡ ጥበብ፡ ወተግ</hi>ሣጽ፡  ዘጸሐፍኩ፡  ውስተ፡  ዝ<hi rend="rubric">ንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አነ፡ ኢያሱ፡  ሲ</hi>ራክ፡ ወልደ፡ አልዐዛር፡  ዘኢየሩሳሌም፡ ሥርዋ፡ ለጥበብ፡ ፈሪሃ፡ እግዚአብሔር፨</incipit>
                                 <note>Book of Sirach. The title is added above the
                                    ornamental band, in a later hand.</note>
                                   <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/M45IAW7J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1861VetTest"/><title level="m">Biblia Veteris Testamenti Aethiopica, in quinque tomos distributa, ad librorum manuscriptorum fidem edidit et apparatu critico instruxit Dr. A.D., Professor Kiliensis. Veteris Testamenti Aethiopici Tomus Secundus sive Libri Regum, Paralipomenon, Esdrae, Esther ad librorum manuscriptorum fidem edidit et apparatu critico instruxit Dr. A.D., Professor Kiliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Christian Friedrich August</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Dillmann</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Lipsiae</pubPlace><publisher>Sumptibus Societatis Germanorum Orientalis, Typis F. A. Brockhausii</publisher><date>1861</date><note type="url">http://digitale-sammlungen.ulb.uni-bonn.de/content/titleinfo/69282</note></bibl>
                                  </msItem>

                                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                                <locus from="60ra" to="79vc"/>
                                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1672Isaiah">Book of Isaiah<hi rend="rubric">ኢሳይያስ</hi></title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ራእየ፡ ዘርእየ፡ ኢሳይያስ፡ ወልደ፡ አሞጽ፡ ዘርእየ፡ በእንተ፡ ይሁዳ፡ ወበእንተ፡ ኢየ</hi>ሩሳሌም፨</incipit>
                                    <explicit xml:lang="gez">ወይሬእዩ፡ አብድንቲሆሙ፡ ለእለ፡ ዐለዉኒ፡ ወዕፄሆሙ፡ ዘይነውም፡ ወእሳቶሙ፡ ዘኢይጠፍእ፡ ወይከውኑ፡ አርአያ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ዘሥጋ፨
                                  </explicit>
                                  <note>Book of Isaiah.</note>
                                  </msItem>

                                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                                     <locus from="80ra" to="104vc"/>
                                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2035Jerem">ኤርምያስ፡ነብይ</title>
                                     <note>The Cycle of Jeremiah. The title is written above the
                                     ornamental band. Cues - names of the Hebrew letters ff. 100r</note>
                                       <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/GE34C4XW"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1894VetTest"/><title level="m">Biblia Veteris Testamenti Aethiopica: in quinque tomos distributa, ad librorum manuscriptorum fidem edidit et apparatu critico instruxit,&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt; V: &lt;/hi&gt;Libri Apocryphi, Baruch, Epistola Jeremiae, Tobith, Judith, Ecclesiasticus, Sapientia, Esdrae Apocalypsis, Esdrae Graecus</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Christian Friedrich August</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Dillmann</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Christian Friedrich August</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Dillmann</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Berolini</pubPlace><publisher>Prostat apud A. Asher et Socios</publisher><date>1894</date><note type="url">http://digitale-sammlungen.ulb.uni-bonn.de/content/titleinfo/69640</note></bibl>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i6.1">
                                  <locus from="80ra" to="100vc"/>
                                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1685Bookof">Book of Jeremiah</title>
                              <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘኮነ፡ ኀበ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ ወልደ፡ ኬልቅዩ፡ ዘእምካህናት፡ </hi>ዘይነብር፡ ውስተ፡
                               አናቶት፡ በብሔረ፡ ብንያም። ወኮነ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <hi rend="rubric">ኀቤየ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ኢዮስያስ፡ ወልደ፡ አሞጽ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ይሁዳ፡ አመ፡ ዓሠርቱ፡ </hi>ወሠለስቱ፡ አመተ፡ መንግሥቱ።  ወኮነ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ኢዮአቂም፡
                              </incipit>
                                  <explicit xml:lang="gez">እስከ፡  ዕለተ፡ ሞቱ፡ በኵሉ፡ መዋዕለ፡ ሕይወቱ፨</explicit>                    
                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i6.2">
                                 <locus from="101v" to="104vc"/>
                                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2167Parali">4 Baruch (Paralipomena of Jeremiah)</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ተረፋተ፡ ነገር፡ ዘባሮክ፡ ወኢ</hi>ኮነ፡ ኅቡእ፡
                                  ዘአመ፡፡ፄወዉ፡ ባ<hi rend="rubric">ቢሎን፡ ወኮነ፡ ሶበ፡ ፄወውዎሙ፡</hi> ለደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡፡ንጉሠ፡፡ከ<hi rend="rubric">ለድዮን፡</hi></incipit>
                                  <explicit xml:lang="gez">ነዋ፡ ጽሕፍት፡ ውስተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ባሮክ፨</explicit>
                                <colophon xml:lang="gez" xml:id="coloph6">
                                  <locus target="#104vc"/>ተፈጸመ፡ በዝየ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ባሮክ፡ ወትሩፋተ፡ ነገሩ፡ ለኤርምያስ፨
                                </colophon>                      
                                </msItem>

                                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                                       <locus from="105ra" to="122vc"/>
                                       <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5801EzekI#Text">No item: LIT5801EzekI, could not check for Text<hi rend="rubric">ሕዝቅኤል</hi></title>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                     <hi rend="rubric">ወኮነ፡ አመ፡ ሣልስ፡ ክረምት፡</hi> በራብዕ፡ ወርኅ፡ በኀሙስ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ሠርቅ፡ ወሀሎኩ፡ ማእከለ፡ </hi>ፄዋ፡ በፈለገ፡ ኮቦር፨</incipit>
                                      <explicit xml:lang="gez"/>
                                      <note>Explanations of some Hebrew names and
                                        words at the end are lacking. At the end of the last
                                      column, the scribe had to compress the writing.</note>
                                    </msItem>


