                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3581Bookof">The First Book of Ezra</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">አመ፡ ሠላሳ፡ ዓመት፡ እም</hi>ዘወድቀት፡ ሃገርነ፡ ወሀለ<hi rend="rubric">ውኩ፡ ውስተ፡ ባቢሎን፡ አነ፡</hi> ሱትኤል፡ ዘተሠመይኩ፡ ዕ<hi rend="rubric">ዝራ፡ </hi></incipit>
